message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as it deals with sound and audio processing. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition, which are related to audio classification. cs.LG is another possible sub-category as it deals with machine learning and neural networks. cs.CV is also possible as it deals with computer vision and image processing, which can be applied to spectrograms. cs.AI is less likely but still possible as it deals with artificial intelligence and machine learning.
